{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"WOW! Dengan CIAYO Stream, Kamu Bisa Main Game PC High End Di Ponsel!","content":"<p>Popularitas game <em>mobile</em> sudah semakin besar dan mengakar. Semakin banyak orang yang bermain game di ponsel alih-alih di konsol rumahan maupun komputer. Berbagai kompetisi game <em>mobile</em> diadakan di tingkat nasional dan internasional.</p>\n<p>Namun, ada beberapa kendala yang dihadapi oleh game <em>mobile</em>. Pertama, tidak semua orang punya ponsel yang cukup kuat memainkan game <em>mobile</em> dengan grafis tinggi. Kedua, judul-judul game <em>mobile</em> tidak sementereng judul-judul game PC, dan kapasitas grafisnya juga terbatas.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48057\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48057\" data-attachment-id=\"48057\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/01-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48057\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48057\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>Adakah solusi bagi para gamer <em>mobile</em> untuk bermain game kualitas AAA di ponsel mereka? Untuk menjawab pertanyaan ini, CIAYO Corp. mempersembahkan CIAYO Stream! CIAYO Stream adalah sebuah aplikasi ponsel yang memungkinkan <em>gamer</em> untuk bermain game PC kualitas tinggi di ponsel, kapan saja dan dimana saja.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"border: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1617482934%2Fvideos%2F10214224215992152%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=560\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>“CIAYO Corp. sebagai sebuah <em>tech company</em> lokal yang selalu berusaha menghadirkan <em>breakthrough</em> untuk perkembangan teknologi di tanah air kita, mengeluarkan produk inovatif baru untuk masa depan, CIAYO Stream, sebuah app dan platform untuk streaming game PC ke mobile devices sehari2 kita,” ungkap Victorio Primadi, Founder dan CTO CIAYO Corp.</p>\n<p>Victorio menambahkan, tujuan dari CIAYO Stream adalah untuk memberikan kesempatan bagi semua pengguna <em>mobile devices</em> untuk dapat menikmati <em>content</em> berkualitas berbasis <em>desktop</em> yang tadinya hanya dapat diakses dengan PC <em>high-end</em> yang mahal.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48058\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48058\" data-attachment-id=\"48058\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/02-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48058\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48058\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan CIAYO Stream, <em>gamer</em> tak perlu khawatir dengan ponsel mereka yang tak sekuat berbagai ponsel jenis <em>flagship</em>. Dengan teknologi <em>streaming</em>, <em>gamer</em> bisa menggunakan ponsel <em>mid sampai hi-end, </em>bahkan <em>Android TV box</em> untuk bermain game dengan kualitas grafis komputer <em>high end</em>! Dengan aksesori tambahan seperti <em>joystick</em>, <em>keyboard</em>, dan <em>mouse</em>, <em>gamer</em> bisa bermain dengan totalitas penuh.</p>\n<p>“Dengan mengikuti dan mengamati perkembangan teknologi global yang semuanya sudah serba <em>mobile</em>, kami percaya bahwa tidak jauh di masa depan, kita akan segera transisi ke era <em>streaming</em>, di mana konektivitas internet sudah memadai dan merata, di saat itu lah kita tidak perlu lagi mendownload konten, baik game, film maupun musik, tetapi semuanya bisa dilakukan dengan <em>streaming</em>,” jelas Victorio.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48059\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48059\" data-attachment-id=\"48059\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/03-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48059\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48059\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>CIAYO Stream menyediakan <em>library</em> game terbitan <em>publisher</em> internasional yang beragam. <em>Gamer</em> juga bisa meng-<em>import</em> <em>library</em> game mereka dari layanan <em>gaming</em> populer seperti Steam, Uplay, Origin, Battle.net, dan masih banyak lagi. “Saat ini kami masih terus memperkaya konten game yang akan tersedia di <em>library</em> CIAYO Stream, yang pasti kami akan hadirkan game-game baru setiap bulannya,” tambah Victorio. Ia juga tengah membuka lebar kesempatan kerja sama dengan berbagai publisher lokal dan luar negeri untuk memasukkan game mereka ke dalam CIAYO Stream.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48060\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48060\" data-attachment-id=\"48060\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/04-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48060\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48060\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>Gamer bisa bermain game di CIAYO Stream secara solo, maupun ditonton oleh jutaan penonton lewat fitur <em>Interactive Livestream</em>. Menariknya, para penonton bisa ikut terlibat secara interaktif dengan memberikan <em>power up</em> ataupun rintangan untuk diatasi oleh <em>gamer</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48061\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48061\" data-attachment-id=\"48061\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/05-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48061\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48061\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>Di CIAYO Stream, <em>gamer</em> juga bisa mendapatkan berbagai hadiah menarik! Setiap <em>achievement</em> yang didapatkan di dalam game, dapat ditukar dengan voucher atau diskon belanja di berbagai <em>merchant</em> populer di Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48062\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48062\" data-attachment-id=\"48062\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/06-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48062\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/06-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48062\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>Tak hanya <em>streaming</em> game, CIAYO Stream juga menyediakan layanan <em>streaming</em> musik, film, dan juga serial TV favorit. Fitur <em>Interactive Livestream</em> juga bisa dimanfaatkan untuk berinteraksi dengan penonton, baik lewat <em>chatting</em> dengan stiker menarik, atau dengan berbagai <em>virtual gift</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48063\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48063\" data-attachment-id=\"48063\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-stream-game-pc-di-ponsel/attachment/07-ciayo-stream/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-ciayo-stream\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48063\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CIAYO Stream\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/07-ciayo-stream-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48063\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Corp.</p></div></p>\n<p>“<em>Interactive Livestream</em> di CIAYO Stream ini tidak terbatas pada aktivitas <em>gaming</em> saja,” kata Victorio. “Apabila kamu adalah seorang kreatif atau pekerja seni, kamu bisa <em>livestream</em> aktivitas kamu dalam berkarya, bisa menunjukkan WIP (Work in-Progress) kamu ke <em>fans</em> &amp; <em>followers</em> kamu dan mereka juga dapat memberikan dukungan ke kamu berupa <em>virtual gifts</em> yang dapat kamu uangkan nantinya.”</p>\n<p>CIAYO Stream saat ini masih dalam tahap pengembangan, serta membuka peluang kerja sama dengan pihak investor, <em>telco</em>, produser film, label musik, merchant e-commerce, para author kreatif, dan para <em>stakeholder</em> lain. “Apabila kami sudah menemukan <em>partner</em> yang tepat dan semuanya lancar, <em>app</em> CIAYO Stream akan tersedia untuk umum di platform iOS &amp; Android pada akhir tahun 2018 ini atau awal 2019,” ungkap Victorio. Victorio juga berharap para developer dan publisher game di Indonesia, baik <em>mobile</em> maupun PC bisa dirangkul agar karya game mereka bisa dinikmati oleh seluruh <em>gamer</em> tanah air lewat CIAYO Stream.</p>\n<p>Entah itu untuk main game, mendengarkan musik, nonton film, atau live broadcast; semua kebutuhan <em>streaming</em> kamu bisa dipenuhi lewat CIAYO Stream!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b62f1949-b05e-5283-a641-2636b7ffd53b"}}}